    "description": "The Thales Advanced Security Platform is a Thales Group (Thales) multi-chip embedded FIPS 140-2 Validated cryptographic module inside the payShield 10000 family of hardware security modules used in the Banking and Finance sector to secure card-based payment transactions. TASP provides functionality for secure loading and/or upgrading of applications used in a range of Thales products. The module ensures tamper resistance and that only applications that have been cryptographically signed by Thales can be loaded into the module.",
